message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously crafted to provide exceptional value and quality. This item is not just a product; it's an experience designed to elevate your daily routine. Considering its unique features and the craftsmanship involved, I believe it's worth more than its face value. I kindly propose a price of $120 for this product. I understand that its true value might be subjective, but I trust that you'll appreciate its worth. Thank you for considering my offer.
